snippet.title: Custom Street World Tour Map Pack 1.0 Now Available!
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD NOW: https://github.com/FortuneStreetModding/CustomStreetWorldTour

Custom Street World Tour 1.0 (or CSWT for short) is a map pack for Fortune Street and Boom Street containing 135 new maps on top of the original 18, including boards from other Itadaki Street games and many original creations from our talented board creators! These boards include custom soundtracks and even some custom backgrounds.

If you'd like a look at what boards are included in CSWT 1.0, please check this video: https://youtu.be/qNWvz4pTrOk

Or you can look at our full map repository here: https://fortunestreetmodding.github.io/maps

Custom Street World Tour was created by the efforts of Deflaktor, Sophilautia and Landmaster, with contributions from 18 other map makers.

If you need help installing, or you'd like to contribute to our community, please consider joining our Discord: https://discord.gg/DE9Hn7T

ABOUT THESE MODS
==================
This footage was recorded using Fixed Fun's HD Texture Pack: https://youtu.be/kl8rTjmgN4s

Multiply Game Speed & 60fps Codes by nikkums: These two codes are an improved version of the previous Speedhack, which aims to make the game run in 60fps with increased speed, similar to Itadaki Street for PS4, but with animations and control displaying more normally than before. A version of this code exists for Wii consoles that keeps the game at the 30fps it can render while speeding up the pace of the gameplay like the 60fps version showcased in this video does. For this video, we are playing in 2x speed. Check our Discord or the video linked above for these codes.

ABOUT THE MOD CREATORS
========================
Deflaktor: https://github.com/Deflaktor

Sophilautia:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/sophilautia
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/sophilautia
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/sophilautia

Landmaster: https://github.com/Landmaster

Special thanks:
mask1n: https://twitter.com/mask1n
nikkums: https://twitter.com/n1kkums
